{"tid":1538744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最心痛是 撤得太遲","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:46:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:41:20.000Z","uid":231977,"like":278,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"978b43e369acf6130697be7e822062c789bcedec","tid":1538744,"uid":231977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:46:41.000Z","msg":"垃圾港共政府諗住依家先黎正式撤回條例扮哂野回應訴求，想攞返民意？想行動降溫？想啱啱燃起嘅時代革命之火胎死腹中？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">收皮啦你屌你老母閪</span><br />\n<br />\n真係太遲啦，遲到我地已經付出差唔多十條嘅人命，多過一千人被捕甚至被起訴葬失前途，無數嘅鮮血同不公平嘅對待，承受恐佈份子嘅暴力襲擊！<br />\n<br />\n但係，喚醒咗我地反抗嘅嗰把火！對呢個腐敗嘅政治體制，喪心病狂嘅警隊，卑鄙無恥嘅中共，我地唔可以坐以待斃！如果依家就收手，大家甘心咩？<br />\n不過林鄭可能太睇得自己，呢兩個月嗌五大訴求多啲定撤回惡法多啲？<br />\n<br />\n最後，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span> 呢句口號絕對唔轉得，係代表緊我地一直以來嘅堅持！<br />\n<strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong>"},{"pid":"0c3d4c493d49bcfe116b7f7c7147b357d5c48a1b","tid":1538744,"uid":231977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:51:26.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"25033a175e21250fd1fdf29e8e22518f1787042a","tid":1538744,"uid":231977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:51:48.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"4621dd0c682fb879b9259f4aab3eb589ebde04da","tid":1538744,"uid":231909,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:51:55.000Z","msg":"提提你<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hZ1WxRh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhZ1WxRh.jpg&h=bdd2d1ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17600b6cff1af0e814eb3e2171b49db19b6dbe5a","tid":1538744,"uid":199235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0c3d4c493d49bcfe116b7f7c7147b357d5c48a1b","tid":1538744,"uid":231977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:51:26.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:51:58.000Z","msg":"缺一不可"},{"pid":"2bfd467691678713ddda2764ba3a43334a99e230","tid":1538744,"uid":231977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,